summary: I think Liefeld may have plagiarized your Character X, man. '___'
question: I think Liefeld may have plagiarized your Character X, man. '___'
answer:
I’LL SUE THEM. I’LL SUE THEM ALL.

Character X can be found here.

I still cannot fucking believe they made the goddamn cat a “thing”. The fact that Carol had a cat was just a little character quirk, and the fact that the cat was actually dimension hopping, because it came from the House of M reality, was just a stupid continuity bit worthy of an obscure trivia challenge.

But KSD made it a THING. Because she had so little planned for Carol, so few things to say about that character, that she focused more on building the fucking cat’s mythology.
